short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Extends the available playback rate options on YouTube.com

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is a very simple Chrome extension that extends the available playback rate options provided by YouTube. Unlike some other extensions this one feels native, does not contain any bloat, and works with the standard YouTube UI/UX and keyboard shortcuts.

YouTube Shortcuts: https://support.google.com/youtube/answer/7631406
